meta.prompt: Link stands at a sketchy-looking wooden kiosk in the Lost Woods, labeled “Tingle’s Totally Legal Rupee Exchange – Best Rates!”. Tingle, wearing sunglasses and a pinstripe suit over his usual green onesie, is handing Link a single giant glittery rupee in exchange for an entire satchel full of small ones. Link has a skeptical eyebrow raised. In the background, Skull Kids are peeking from behind trees, snickering. Shafts of mysterious green light beam through the forest canopy, casting dramatic light over this absurdly shady transaction. The scene has a magical but hilariously suspicious vibe.
